<br>
I figured this out while pulling last night... if I need to FD again quickly, I leave the mouse pointer over the hotkey.  The problem was it therefore stayed yellow, which means FD refreshed but I didn't realize it.<br>
<br>
Btw... I understand I could simply use the #s on the keyboard but I prefer to mainly use by gamepad/mouse combo.<br>
<br>
Any suggestions?  I assume you can change the default hotkey color or the highlight color?  Anyone know how...<br>
